# Artwall - Vertical Printing Website

A modern and responsive website showcasing vertical printing services. This project is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript,and use of **Tilt.js** to create 3D tilt effects for elements. Designed for fast and user-friendly interactions.

---

## 🌟 Features
- Interactive hero section with animations.
- Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop.
- Gallery showcasing vertical printing services.
- Call-to-action buttons for easy navigation.
- Smooth 3D tilt effects on hover.
- Fully responsive and compatible with modern browsers.

---

## 🚀 Technologies Used
- **HTML5**: For the structure of the website.
- **CSS3**: For styling and animations.
- **JavaScript**: For interactivity and dynamic functionality.

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

├── index.html         # Main HTML file
├── css/
│   ├── styles.css     # Main CSS file
├── js/
│   ├── script.js      # Main JavaScript file
├── assets/
│   ├── images/        # Folder containing images

---

## 📖 Usage

1. **Clone the Repository**:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Nelson-Lamounier/artwall.git
   cd artwall

   	2.	Open in Browser:
Open index.html in your favorite browser to view the site.
	3.	Customizing:
	•	Edit css/styles.css to adjust the styles.
	•	Edit js/script.js for interactivity.

